text: Mano, why do you like parks and such?

...Sorry for asking suddenly.
It's not like I'm forcing you to tell me or anything...

N-No, it's okay...
Um, well, you see...

...On days like today with nice weather,
it feels good to sit on a bench and soak up the sun...

...Um, well...
S-Sorry for saying weird things...

I don't mind at all.
Being able to express yourself like that, Mano, is amazing.

I... I actually want to hear more...
About your feelings and thoughts, Mano...
